Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time spent in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of cases starting with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Maximum time spent in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before moving to any next activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002583FC292D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call' across cases where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Closed' for cases including both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - User' in cases where this transition occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases leading to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to the next activity for cases involving 'PROD582'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Assigned' for cases with low impact products
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' for cases that transition to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Difference in average time spent in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' between cases initiated by 'V30' group and 'C9' group
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:group filtered by the function ma == 'V30' where ma is the last value of org:group

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call' for cases with high impact products
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
